ROOT Password RESET :
---------------------

1)power on virtual machine

2) As soon as possiable press (ctrl + Alt +delete)

3)select down arrow and select(Redhat enterprise linux (0-rescue-..............) (we are recovering the root password from grub)

4)And press e (edit)

5)And we can see different screen .Select down arrow button and go for the line where linux is written) and give end button we can to end of
that line and type

 --> rd.break  console=tty1  selinux=0 
 
6) And press (ctrl+x)  --->to start

7)Then it will ask 
 
      -------->press enter for maintainance (or ctrl+d to continue): enter
	  
8)we are in read only mode we need to go for read and write mode for changing of root password that's why we are remounting the file system.

     --------->mount -o remount,rw /sysroot/
	 
9)pwd we are in /root but we need go for higher level so :

   chroot /sysroot/
   
10) All are set  After that just type passwd and type your root passwd.

    passwd 

11)exit ,exit 

12) And system will start booting.
